{"article_id":"OhY0tNOhCXGKWRVA","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"It looks like Senate Democrats now have the votes","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"they need","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"to pass a resolution","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that would block President Donald Trump ' s national emergency declaration","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"to fund his border wall .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Four Republicans","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"- Sens . Susan Collins , Thom Tillis , Lisa Murkowski , and Rand Paul -","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"have said","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"they plan to vote in favor","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"of terminating the national emergency ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"giving Democrats the 51-vote majority","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"they need","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"to approve the resolution in the upper chamber .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell acknowledged just as much during a Monday press appearance ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"though he emphasized","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"that Congress wouldn ' t have the votes","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"to override a presidential veto ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"which Trump is expected to use ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"CBS News ' s Mark Knoller reports .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Republicans hold a bare three-seat majority in the Senate ,","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"which means Democrats must stay united","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"and peel off at least four Republicans","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"( Vice President Mike Pence could come in with a tie-breaking vote )","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"to get this resolution passed .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"Paul announced this weekend","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"that he intends to vote","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"to block the emergency ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"making him the fourth Republican","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"to do so .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Paul ' s also far from the only Republican","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"who could still go against Trump .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"In addition to the Republicans","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"who ' ve already said how they plan to vote ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Democrats are watching a number of others","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"who could cross the aisle ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"many of whom cited concerns about the declaration ' s constitutionality and the precedent","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"it could set for future presidents ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Politico reports .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"This resolution","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"- which has already passed the House -","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"gives Congress the ability","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"to end the emergency .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Since Trump is set to veto it , however ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"it ' s not expected to ultimately go into effect .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"( Two-thirds of members of both the House and Senate are needed","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"to override a veto . )","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"Despite this likely outcome ,","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"a congressional rebuke of Trump ' s actions would be significant","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"and highlight how many members of his own party also disagree with his actions .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Additionally , it could provide more fodder for court cases","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"centered on the national emergency ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"since it would explicitly highlight Congress ' s opposition to this declaration .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"What ' s more , it ' s unclear if Trump would actually follow through on a veto ,","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"since he has yet to use his veto powers in his presidency .","depth":4},{"id":54,"text":"While it remains to be seen just how many Senate Republicans will also come forward on the matter ,","depth":3},{"id":55,"text":"here ' s a rundown of lawmakers","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"to watch .","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"Susan Collins","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"( ME ) :","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"Collins was the first Republican","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"to say","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"she would back a resolution","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"blocking the emergency .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"\" If it ' s a ' clean ' disapproval resolution ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"I will support it , \"","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"she said recently ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"according to an Associated Press report .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Thom Tillis","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"( NC ) :","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Tillis outlined his reasons","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"for backing a resolution","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"terminating the emergency","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"in a recent Washington Post op-ed .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"He especially emphasized","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"that this declaration could open the floodgates for the use of national emergencies down the line .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"\" Conservatives should take these warnings seriously , \"","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"he writes .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"\" They should be thinking about whether they would accept the prospect of a President Bernie Sanders","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"declaring a national emergency","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"to implement parts of the radical Green New Deal ;","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"a President Elizabeth Warren","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"declaring a national emergency","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"to shut down banks","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"and take over the nation ' s financial institutions ;","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"or a President Cory Booker","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"declaring a national emergency","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"to restrict Second Amendment rights . \"","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"Lisa Murkowski","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"( AK ) :","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Murkowski indicated","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"that she is \" likely \" to support a resolution","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"blocking the emergency , a sentiment","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"she expressed in a recording","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"obtained by the Associated Press .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"\" I want to make sure","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"that the resolution of disapproval is exactly what I think","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"it is ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"because","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"if it is","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"as I understand it to be ,","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"I will likely be supporting the resolution","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"to disapprove of the action , \"","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Rand Paul","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"( KY ) :","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"Paul has said","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"he was \" disappointed \" with the president ' s decision","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"to go this route","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"and this weekend announced","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"that he would vote in favor of a resolution","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"terminating the emergency .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"\" I can ' t vote to give the president the power","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"to spend money","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"that hasn ' t been appropriated by Congress , \"","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"he said during a Saturday speech ,","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"the Bowling Green Daily News reports .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"\" We may want more money for border security ,","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"but Congress didn ' t authorize it .","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"If we take away those checks and balances ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"it ' s a dangerous thing . \"","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"Lamar Alexander","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"( TN ) :","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"Alexander laid out an alternative option for the Trump administration on Thursday :","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"find the money for the wall elsewhere .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"\" I want to make a respectful suggestion ,","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"and that is this :","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"that President Trump ask his lawyers to take a second look at an existing funding authority","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"that the president has to consider construction of the 234 miles of border wall","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"that do not require a formal declaration of a national emergency , \"","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"he said in a floor speech .","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"If the Trump administration did this ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"it may not even have to face a failed vote on the emergency ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"he seemed to indicate .","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"Alexander , however , did not say just exactly how he ' ll vote ,","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"according to BuzzFeed News .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"\" I learned a long time ago in the United States Senate ,","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"it ' s not wise to announce how you ' ll vote on a vote","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"you may never have to take , \"","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"Roger Wicker","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"( MS ) :","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"Before Trump declared a national emergency ,","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"Wicker was among the Republicans","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"who expressed misgivings","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"about using this tactic","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"to obtain funding .","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"\" I would be inclined to vote for the resolution of disapproval , \"","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"Wicker said in an interview with HuffPost earlier in February .","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"He hasn ' t offered an update since .","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"Marco Rubio","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"( FL ) :","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"Rubio was among the first Republicans","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"to highlight challenges","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"a national emergency declaration could pose the president ,","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"noting","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"that it could clash with Congress ' s constitutionally designated \" power of the purse. \"","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"\" We have a crisis at our southern border ,","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"but no crisis justifies violating the Constitution , \"","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"Rubio previously said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"\" Today ' s national emergency is border security .","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"But a future president may use this exact same tactic","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"to impose the Green New Deal . \"","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"Rubio hasn ' t said how he ' ll vote on a resolution yet , however .","depth":6},{"id":163,"text":"Mitt Romney","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"( UT ) :","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"Romney has also indicated","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"that he is not fully on board with the national emergency ,","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"though he ' s said","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"he needs to finish reviewing the resolution","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"before deciding on a vote .","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"\" I do not believe","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"declaring a national emergency is the right approach , \"","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"Romney has said in the past ,","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"according to the Salt Lake Tribune .","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"Others potential GOP swing votes include Jerry Moran","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"( KS ) ,","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"Mike Lee","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"( UT ) ,","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"and Cory Gardner","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"( CO ) ,","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"according to the Hill and Politico .","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"Trump , meanwhile , has suggested","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"that Republicans","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"who vote against him on the issue","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"could put themselves in a tough electoral position .","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"\" I really think","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"that Republicans","depth":15},{"id":187,"text":"that vote against border security and the wall ,","depth":15},{"id":188,"text":"I think","depth":15},{"id":189,"text":"you know ,","depth":16},{"id":190,"text":"I ' ve been okay at predicting things ,","depth":16},{"id":191,"text":"I think","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"they put themselves at great jeopardy , \"","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"he said during a Fox News interview .","depth":10},{"id":194,"text":"The Senate needs to vote on the resolution within 18 days","depth":9},{"id":195,"text":"of receiving it from the House ,","depth":9},{"id":196,"text":"given the procedure","depth":9},{"id":197,"text":"outlined in the National Emergencies Act .","depth":9},{"id":198,"text":"Since the House just passed the resolution last Tuesday ,","depth":8},{"id":199,"text":"there ' s still some time","depth":9},{"id":200,"text":"before Senate Republicans will have to make their final decision .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":401,"left":254,"right":400,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":254,"left":238,"right":253,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":219,"right":237,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":205,"right":218,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":202,"right":204,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":2,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"N